MdCalculate

Source: R/AllCcsMdFun.R
MdCalculate.Rd

MdCalculate

MdCalculate(mol_smiles, mol_names)

Arguments

mol_smiles

a smiles structure of molecule
mol_names

the name of structure

Examples

MdCalculate(mol_smiles = "COC1=CC=C(CC(O)=O)C=C1", mol_names = "4-Methoxyphenylacetic Acid")
